						<summary>

						<p>On two pieces of a broken stone lying near the Rāmasvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śrāvaṇa, śu. 1, Monday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Registers the gift of land made as <hi rend="italic">nūtimānya</hi> by Pōlēpalli Bū • • • • • dēva-Mahārāja to Ayya Reḍḍi, son of Kaḍapa Anni-Reḍḍi.</p>						

